initLoggingProperties

protected void initLoggingProperties()
Initialise the logging properties for the Protege engine. Normally, Protege picks these up from the file defined by the System property 
java.util.logging.config.file
Using 3 servlet context parameters, set the logging level for:
  • protege_system_log - the Protege system logger, protege.system
  • protege_file_handler - the file log handler
  • protege_console_handler - the console log handler
These have values defined by java.util.logging.Level
